channel.title: 718 NPC help Nulls
channel.description: Hey when i talk to most of my npcs it says null and examine shows id pos and null, but it looks like the real thing, how would i change the npc because my unpackedspawn.txt is weird i add a npc it doesn't spawn it... help me please.

item.title: 718 NPC help Nulls
item.dc:creator: @nikolaww3 nikolaww3
item.description:
@nikolaww3 wrote:

[quote=“Yozora, post:2, topic:449698”]You need to delete the packedNPC folder after you make changes to the unpackedspawn.txt file. A new folder will be generated at run time.[/quote]Yeah thanks it spawned but not all the other npcs… good thing i backed it up

item.title: 718 NPC help Nulls
item.dc:creator: @Yozora Yozora
item.description:
@Yozora wrote:

You need to delete the packedNPC folder after you make changes to the unpackedspawn.txt file. A new folder will be generated at run time.
